- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is another possible category as the paper describes a tool that can aid in software development by automatically generating and discovering new lemmas. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses a system that uses automated techniques to discover new lemmas and aid in proof automation.
